---
title: Bacon and Portobello Mushroom Pie with a Crispy Crumb Topping
description: The Guiness world record for the most expensive pie was sold for £1,024 per slice! It was made with Japanese wagyu beef, Chinese matsutake mushrooms, Winter black mushrooms, and French bluefoot mushrooms! And while our pie isn’t quite as extravagant, it sure is tasty. A real family favourite, children through to adults will love this wholesome and comforting pie.
